#

Miso-Glazed Pork Chops with Sautéed Bok Choy and Jasmine Rice

$15.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Asian-InspiredComfort FoodEasy Dinner

Description

Tender pork chops glazed in umami-rich miso, served with vibrant sautéed bok choy and fragrant jasmine rice.

Ingredients

  • Pork chops: 4 pieces
  • White miso paste: 3 tablespoons
  • Soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • Honey: 1 tablespoon
  • Sesame oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Garlic cloves: 2, minced
  • Ginger: 1 inch, grated
  • Bok choy: 2 heads, chopped
  • Jasmine rice: 1 cup
  • Water: 2 cups
  • Green onions: for garnish
  • Sesame seeds: for garnish
